与死神抢人的“气切小分队”：稍有不慎就是致命威胁。
With death rob the "gas cut team": a little carelessness is a deadly threat.
澎湃新闻                      。
The news is roaring.
澎湃新闻。
The news is roaring.
有内涵的时政新媒体。
Connotation of the new political media.
澎湃新闻记者 朱轩 通讯员 杜巍巍 邹亚琴“下手术刀后，胸腔气流会携带着新冠病毒喷出。
Peng Pai reporter Zhu Xuan correspondent Duwei Zou Ya Qin "after the operating knife, chest airflow will carry the new crown virus ejected.
医生首先需要切开甲状软骨下缘，暴露气管；再切开气管前壁，迅速插入气管套管，将硅胶内管从套管植入并固定，接上呼吸机……”这一系列精准操作需要在15分钟内完成。
Doctors first need to cut the lower edge of the thyroid cartilage to expose the trachea; then cut through the front wall of the trachea and insert it rapidly into the trachea cannula, implanting and securing the silica tube from the casing and attaching to the ventilator... "
“65，80，97”，床边监护仪上的动脉血氧饱和度迅速飙升，患者生命体征重回稳定。
"65, 80, 97." Blood oxygen saturation on the bedside monitor soared and the patient's vital signs returned to stability.
这是武汉大学人民医院东院区医生为新冠肺炎危重患者做气管切开手术时的场景。
This is the scene when doctors in the East Hospital of Wuhan University performed tracheotomy for patients with severe pneumonia.
武汉大学人民医院东院区“气切小分队”正在为患者进行气管切开手术 来源：武汉大学人民医院东院区澎湃新闻（www.thepaper.cn）2月28日从武汉大学人民医院东院区获悉，28日下午，在与死神的“抢人”大战中，该院耳鼻喉科主任朱霆带领的3人党员“气切小分队”（新冠肺炎患者气管切开手术小分队）又一次获得了胜利。
The hospital's head of ear, nose and throat, Zhu Ting, led a three-member team that won the battle against death in the afternoon of Feb. 28, according to the East Campus of Wuhan University's People's Hospital.
截至2月28日，“气切小分队”已完成了5例针对新冠肺炎危重症患者的气管切开手术。
As of February 28, the gas-cut team had completed five tracheotomy operations in critically ill patients with Newcomial Pneumonia.
据介绍，对于已进行气管插管的新冠肺炎危重症患者来说，如果7-10天内不能拔管，就需要做气管切开手术。
Patients with severe coronary pneumonia who have had a trachea intubation may require a tracheotomy if they cannot be removed within 7-10 days, it said.
而手术时，大量分泌物气溶胶会喷出，患者肺内沉积的病毒颗粒也会直接暴露在空气中。
During surgery, a large amount of secretion aerosols can be ejected, the virus particles deposited in the patient's lungs will also be directly exposed to the air.
稍有不慎，对于医护人员来说都是致命威胁。
A little carelessness can be a fatal threat to health care workers.
每次手术前，“气切小分队”的成员们都要做好三级防护，2层防护服、N95口罩、护目镜、脚套……与其他同事不一样的是，他们还要戴上正压头套，同时戴上4层手套。
Before each operation, members of the "gas-cut team" are required to have three levels of protection: two layers of protective clothing, N95 face masks, goggles, and foot covers... unlike other colleagues, they also wear positive headgear and four layers of gloves.
武汉大学人民医院东院区“气切小分队”正在为患者进行气管切开手术 来源：武汉大学人民医院东院区气管切开对主刀医生的视觉与触觉要求很高。
The "gas-cut team" of Wuhan University People's Hospital is performing tracheotomy for patients: The tracheotomy in the East courtyard of Wuhan University People's Hospital requires a high visual and tactile sense of the surgeon.
头套上的水蒸气会阻碍术者的视野；双手戴的4层手套，让执刀的手指几乎感觉不到任何东西。
The water vapor on the hood blocks the surgeon's vision; the hands wear four layers of gloves so that the fingers holding the knife can hardly feel anything.
在视觉与触觉双重“失灵”的情况下，每一次手术，朱霆和队友几乎都全凭经验完成。
In the case of visual and tactile "failure," each surgery, Zhu and team-mates almost entirely by experience.
2月20日，东院区耳鼻喉科接到重症医学科的紧急求助电话。
On February 20, the ENT received an emergency call from the Department of Severe Medicine.
一位70岁新冠肺炎危重症患者气管插管后，血氧饱和度只有60%，亟需气管切开。
After trachea intubation in a 70-year-old patient with severe pneumonia, blood oxygen saturation was only 60% and tracheotomy was urgently needed.
“必须尽快进行气管切开，否则患者很快会因为呼吸衰竭而亡。
"A tracheotomy must be done as soon as possible, or the patient will soon die of respiratory failure.
”重症医学科主任周晨亮与驰援的华西医院重症医学科主任康焰讨论后，决定请“气切小分队”操刀进行气管切开。
Chow Chenliang, director of severe medicine, and Kang Yan, director of severe medicine at Huaxi Hospital, decided to ask the "air-cut team" to carry out tracheotomy.
朱霆带着“气切小分队”成员丁永军、邓智锋换好防护服，第一时间带上气切包赶到了重症医学科病房，与在病房支援的新疆医疗队重症组组长杨建中携手上台。
Zhuting with "gas-cut team" members Ding Yongjun, Deng Zhifeng exchange protective clothing, the first time with gas-cut bags rushed to the intensive care unit, and in the ward support of the Xinjiang Medical Team, Yang Jianzhong took up the stage.
摆体位、铺治疗巾、评估、麻醉、气管切开......一系列精密经皮气管切手术操作、重新连上呼吸机后，患者气道风险降低，舒适度立马改善。
Postures, treatment towels, assessments, anaesthesia, tracheotomy... a series of precise percutaneous tracheotomy operations, re-connection to the ventilator, patients with reduced airway risk, comfort immediately improved.
而“气切小分队”的所有人，全身已被汗水浸透。
The "gas cut team" all over the body has been saturated with sweat.
朱霆表示，对于危重症新冠肺炎患者的抢救，气管切开具有良好的辅助治疗效果。
Zhu said that for the critically ill patients with New Crown Pneumonia rescue tracheotomy has a good therapeutic effect.
“降低危重症新冠肺炎患者的死亡率，需要多个学科共同协作，党员医生更要冲锋在前。
"Reducing mortality in critically ill patients with new crown pneumonia requires collaboration across disciplines, especially among Party members.
只要患者有需要，我们‘气切小分队’一定使命必达！”本期编辑 常琛推荐阅读。
As long as the patient needs, we 'gas cut team' certain mission must achieve! "This issue editor Chang Chen recommends reading.
